payload.sql: SELECT `groups`.`id` AS t0_r0, `groups`.`name` AS t0_r1, `groups`.`short_name` AS t0_r2, `groups`.`position` AS t0_r3, `groups`.`created_at` AS t0_r4, `groups`.`updated_at` AS t0_r5, `groups`.`deleted_at` AS t0_r6, `parameters`.`id` AS t1_r0, `parameters`.`group_id` AS t1_r1, `parameters`.`formula_id` AS t1_r2, `parameters`.`uom_id` AS t1_r3, `parameters`.`name` AS t1_r4, `parameters`.`short_name` AS t1_r5, `parameters`.`position` AS t1_r6, `parameters`.`created_at` AS t1_r7, `parameters`.`updated_at` AS t1_r8, `parameters`.`deleted_at` AS t1_r9, `param_vals`.`id` AS t2_r0, `param_vals`.`parameter_id` AS t2_r1, `param_vals`.`subject_id` AS t2_r2, `param_vals`.`date_time` AS t2_r3, `param_vals`.`val_numeric` AS t2_r4, `param_vals`.`val_string` AS t2_r5, `param_vals`.`created_at` AS t2_r6, `param_vals`.`updated_at` AS t2_r7, `param_vals`.`deleted_at` AS t2_r8 FROM `groups` LEFT OUTER JOIN `parameters` ON `parameters`.`group_id` = `groups`.`id` LEFT OUTER JOIN `param_vals` ON `param_vals`.`parameter_id` = `parameters`.`id` WHERE (`groups`.`deleted_at` IS NULL) AND (param_vals.subject_id in ('100',101,102,103,104,105,106,107,108) AND YEAR(param_vals.date_time) = '2012')
